00:01:05,459 --> 00:01:11,549
So on one occasion, the Blessed One was dwelling at the town of the Melians named Uruvelacapa.

9
00:01:12,751 --> 00:01:19,262
Then Bhadraka, the headman, approached the Blessed One, paid homage to him,

10
