and you get this and the usual uh great praise he's wonderful venerable it's amazing venerable sir how well that was stated by the blessed one see and then he then he tells the buddha what he just heard whatever suffering arises all that is rooted in desire has desire at its source for desire is the root of suffering um that's that's what uh um what's what they call it um therapists do isn't it they they

