96
00:12:08,562 --> 00:12:13,267
But that's not, what you want to do is to absorb these little sentences that you find.

97
00:12:14,229 --> 00:12:17,993
Little paragraphs.

98
00:12:18,013 --> 00:12:18,974
There we are, you see.

99
00:12:19,355 --> 00:12:22,719
Desire, sorry, suffering is rooted in desire.

100
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:23,799
Second noble truth.

101
00:12:26,394 --> 00:12:33,004
I can only hope that these words have finally driven home the truth.

102
00:12:33,024 --> 00:12:37,211
A desire is in fact, a suffering is in fact rooted in desire.

103
00:12:38,211 --> 00:12:46,283
